title: Willie Nelson - Good Times (1969) [FLAC]
description:
downloaded from Qobuz

This is kind of an odd record. One side is very sparse instrumentally, while the other side has three different people providing arrangements. The songs are okay (maybe subpar for Nelson), with one of the most interesting being his cover of Mickey Newbury's "Sweet Memories." ~ Jim Worbois, Allmusic

Tracks:
01 Good Times
02 December Day
03 Sweet Memories
04 Little Things
05 Pages
06 She's Still Gone
07 Ashamed
08 A Wonderful Yesterday
09 Permanently Lonely
10 Down to Our Last Goodbye
11 Buddy
12 Did I Ever Love You
